defs.name: SysctlError
defs.value:
pub enum SysctlError {
    NotFound(String),
    UnknownType,
    ExtractionError,
    ParseError,
    MissingImplementation,
    IoError(std::io::Error),
    Utf8Error(std::str::Utf8Error),
    NoReadAccess,
    NoWriteAccess,
    NotSupported,
    ShortRead {
        read: usize,
        reported: usize,
    },
    InvalidCStr(std::ffi::FromBytesWithNulError),
}
